  dialogueLines:
  - Speaker: Barista
    Text: You came back.
  - Speaker: Rina
    Text: I said I might.
  - Speaker: Barista
    Text: You did. I was curious whether this place would scare you off or not.
  - Speaker: Rina
    Text: It almost did.
  - Speaker: Barista
    Text: Almost is still better than never. What are you having this time?
  choices:
  - choiceText: Something simple. Let me see the menu again.
